      • DMatrix

        public DMatrix(long[] headers,
       long[] indices,
       float[] data,
       DMatrix.SparseType st)
        create DMatrix from sparse matrix
        参数:
        headers - index to headers (rowHeaders for CSR or colHeaders for CSC)
        indices - Indices (colIndexs for CSR or rowIndexs for CSC)
        data - non zero values (sequence by row for CSR or by col for CSC)
        st - sparse matrix type (CSR or CSC)
